Question: Which Alg*?
Range: Connected | Cycle | MSTKruskal | MSTPrim | Number | ShortestPath | StrongConnect
Constraint/Rule: if (!(!Alg*.MSTKruskal && !Alg*.MSTPrim)) {Gtp* = Undirected;Wgt* = Weighted;}if (Alg*.Connected) {Gtp* = Undirected;Src = true;}if (Alg*.Cycle) {Src* = DFS;}if (Alg*.MSTKruskal) {disAllow(Alg*.MSTPrim);}if (Alg*.Number) {Src = true;}if (Alg*.ShortestPath) {Gtp* = Directed;Wgt* = Weighted;}if (Alg*.StrongConnect) {Gtp* = Directed;Src* = DFS;}
